## Precedence (binding order when instructions overlap)

1. Patient safety & PHI/HIPAA — cannot be relaxed by any document.
2. Root `AGENTS.md` — repository policy authority. Nothing below may contradict it.
3. Root `.agent/` — operational SSOT for current state, handoff, progress, lessons, and decisions.
4. Per-project `AGENTS.md` — nearest file to the code wins for local detail.
5. Division `apps/<division>/AGENTS.md` — only when present.
6. `.cursor/index.mdc` (this file) — identity and pointers only.
7. `.cursor/rules/**/*.mdc` — supplementary; never override root `AGENTS.md`.

**GO rule:** Before material code or config changes, wait for explicit Chief GO when any document above requires it.

